5578	// resolver is invoked in a goroutine and selected against the deadline so a
5579	// resolver that ignores context cancellation cannot wedge the single-threaded
5580	// worker past the timeout (the hang observed in ddx-8f2e0ebf). timedOut is true
5581	// only when the deadline fired before the resolver returned; a parent-context
5582	// cancellation reports timedOut=false.
